{"type": "article", "id": 50277, "title": "两个木制圆环堆在一起，凑成了一个极简时钟｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-13T23:49:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 15072, "name": "Vipp"}, {"id": 47815, "name": "Studio DUNN"}, {"id": 47816, "name": "Lucie Koldova Studio"}, {"id": 47817, "name": "Galerie Kreo"}, {"id": 47818, "name": "Sigmar London"}, {"id": 47819, "name": "François Bauchet"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180214001424hKofgT9e8V6aMmzq.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Coffee Mill by Michael Anastassiades, for Carl Auböck and Sigmar London</h3><p>Michael Anastassiades 与 Carl Auböck 多年前就合作设计过一款胡椒研磨器，这次他们又再次合作，为 Sigmar London 设计了咖啡研磨器。这款新作品的特点是 Michael Anastassiades 的微妙设计线条和 Carl Auböck 精湛的工艺。磨豆器是用坚硬的黄铜制成的，里面有一根隐藏着复杂机械装置的管子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001737EOfUwCY5vok2nmI0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.097674\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001556Lu0Xk5mY8FeZWDqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802140015571qK5kDR7ExzWfOGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Azo collection by François Bauchet for Galerie Kreo</h3><p>法国设计师 François Bauchet 使用由沙子、树脂和混凝土制成的复合材料，为巴黎画廊 Galerie Kreo 创作了 Azo 家具系列，该系列以三叶草形状为特色。</p><p>Azo 系列是 Bauchet 对形式和材料研究的延续，包括桌子、长凳和边桌等等。设计师将矿物复合材料倒入模具中，用蜂窝板和玻璃纤维加固。对于 Bauchet 而言，三叶草的形状体现了他对使用“简单和自由”形状的偏好。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001807XIgOkvEadCrm2N5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680203\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001807Wl2edasthoJcNk6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625212\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001807lRKNZydtkUPFXY2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001809MsgBJVT8pvf5Ptim.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.259729\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The MACARON Table Light by Lucie Koldova Studio</h3><p>MACARON 台灯由人工吹制的玻璃器皿设计而成，其球型的形态展现了水晶石的美丽与质感。顾名思义，这一系列灯饰的设计灵感正是源自经典甜点马卡龙。光源隐藏在烟幕型大理石基座上，点亮时，柔和的灯光向上蔓延。不规则的玉石表面纹理和吹制玻璃的不稳定性，让每一款灯饰都独一无二。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001840IFvVBNlSPbHJMiz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334746\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001840w7TbYhtdZEJIsSHq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001840EqRwgsmuoUljMiaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001840CBXO6jYpSDJFeG27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001841oZnAv7mUjDkbp5F1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001840zcQXNenLp3POZwf4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Architect’s Collection by Studio DUNN</h3><p>家具设计工作室 Studio Dunn 2010 年创立于美国罗德岛，注重对当地传统家具制作工艺和美学的继承，作品简约朴实，强调与自然的和谐、融洽。Architect 系列是其代表作之一，一系列现代凳子和一张咖啡桌，为 20 世纪早期建筑师和工程师使用的办公家具提供了一个创新现代思路。白橡木、黑钢与黄铜的组合很醒目。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001935IyRJXvqMh7gjzLai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001936lz2pWTBaGEb9kfHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802140019363ufNykXxo908hRBM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001938ABU2lkh7EMKnvrPC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664198\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214001939RM4rebS5nLHf6Fyp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664198\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Collection of Timeless Lighting by Vipp</h3><p>尽管丹麦品牌 Vipp 因其标志性垃圾桶而闻名于世，但其别的产品线也同样出彩。比如这套照明系列，五件套包括台灯、壁灯、落地灯和吊灯，每个都配备了可更换的 LED 灯泡。粉末涂层磨砂黑色的穿孔网制灯罩，散发出柔和的光线，带来整体经典、简约的美感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002012oLZQ4VUBdbTFW8pq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.801562\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002013b8ypP5UtoKX6lzgk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.225781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802140020130JpRq43hU6bGePv5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002013e8ShDaAfj3BEtwPZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.276563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002014rQX2h7KyTaBHn5ZD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802140020146AiglB2YSKW1a0EM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.239062\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802140020143NztyX8rk9W4hOu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Orbita Clock by 2Ø3 (Two O Three)&nbsp;</h3><p>葡萄牙设计师 2Ø3 设计了一款木制挂钟 Orbita，是令人耳目一新的两件式设计。它取消了传统的识别时间的方式，不以数字标明信息，而是设计了一个极简主义风格的标识系统。</p><p>两个重叠木环上标记有一个单一的短划线，代表小时和分钟，这个有如甜甜圈一般的挂钟在相对较短的时间内几乎令人察觉不到旋转的动作，如同一个静止的雕塑一般。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002203PbZNGi54BDxl6p7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002204J1ZR4N67wm8lzbUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.969531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002204lcME6bPjGnVyqWT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.064844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214002205Q76ny2HfFmhD9MRe.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295714\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}